1. Proving how Greedy fails
************************************************************************************************************************
If we propose Greedy works,
How to find a counter test case that proves Greedy Doesnot work?
=> Eg. [5    50      11]
       [10   100     20] 
We cannot pick same index on two consecutive days. 
Being Greedy => From first row, select i=1 which is 50. Max of all three.
From second row, cannot select i=1 as it is repetitive. Can select i=0 or i=2 => Take Max => 20
Total answer by greedy = 50+20 = 70

But, actual answer = 100 + 11 => 111
This proves that Greedy failed and DP works

